So many theories have been posited as to what might have happened to Bogonko Bosire.In this episode, we follow up on three major theories: Could he be in ICC's protection programme?Could he have left the country and is living elsewhere? Or was he murdered?We also speak to an expert on missing people about what alternative methods his friends and family might have overlooked in the search for the journalist. In Itumbi’s retracing of Bogonko’s last steps before he went missing, he reveals that he had visited a woman in Mwea. Who is she? Crucial time was spent pressuring the police and Dennis Itumbi to produce him. According to family members, the deceased was attached to the DP’s security detail for several years. The footbridge was damaged by a trailer carrying an excavator earlier in December 2020. However they made us feel, the men and women in this list elicited different emotions in all of us.